These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, coffee
There 2 different types of food: lettuce, broccoli
1. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | coffee  | fanta |
| Food       | lettuce | broccoli |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, 7up
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
2. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | mirinda | 7up |
| Sport      | soccer     | water-polo  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, adventure
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, turkish
1. the egyptian is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the egyptian is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | adventure  |
| Nationality   | egyptian | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
