.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-7::.
There are 2 different nationalities: mexican, indian
2 different pets are kept: turtle, mouse
1. the indian is on the left or right of the mexican##3
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Nationality   | mexican | indian |
| Pet           | mouse     | turtle  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-8::.
