The people have 2 different jobs:  security-guard, accountant
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the accountant is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | puzzles |
| Job     | security-guard        | accountant |

