.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-12::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, ice-hockey
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, van
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |
| Sport       | sailing  | ice-hockey |
| Transport   | snowmobile | van |

